<footer id="contact" class="bg-surface-dark text-slate-300">
  <div class="container-main section-padding">
    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <div>
        <div class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-gold text-lg font-bold text-brand-950">H</span>
          <span class="text-xl font-bold text-white">{{brand}}</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-400">
          Cung cấp cho quý khách hệ thống thông tin hoạt động hiệu quả 24/7, từ website giới thiệu công ty, sản phẩm và dịch vụ tới hệ thống email, chăm sóc khách hàng, nhân sự, kế toán và các sản phẩm CNTT khác.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="mb-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Thông tin liên hệ</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-brand-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>
            <span>{{address}}</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-brand-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/></svg>
            <a href="tel:{{phone}}" class="hover:text-white">{{phone}}</a>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-brand-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
            <a href="mailto:{{email}}" class="hover:text-white">{{email}}</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="mb-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Bản tin mới</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          {{#each blogPosts}}
          <li>
            <a href="#blog" class="text-slate-400 transition-colors hover:text-brand-400">{{this.title}}</a>
          </li>
          {{/each}}
        </ul>

        <h3 class="mb-4 mt-8 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Liên kết</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="#services" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-brand-400">Quy trình thiết kế website</a></li>
          <li><a href="#services" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-brand-400">Bảo trì website</a></li>
          <li><a href="#banggia" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-brand-400">Báo giá thiết kế web</a></li>
          <li><a href="#projects" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-brand-400">Dự án mẫu</a></li>
          <li><a href="#blog" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-brand-400">Kiến thức</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 border-t border-slate-700/50 pt-8 text-center text-sm text-slate-500">
      Copyright Ⓒ {{year}} {{brand}}
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
